dashboardQueries.name: c9ef2d39-14a4-4f38-a95b-83692c8595e0
dashboardQueries.query:
metadata.vendor_name="Corelight"
metadata.product_event_type = "conn"
about.resource.attribute.labels["capture_source"] = "vpcflow"
network.ip_protocol != "ICMP" OR (network.ip_protocol = "ICMP" AND re.regex(principal.ip, `.*:.*`))
$date_hour=timestamp.get_timestamp(metadata.event_timestamp.seconds, "%Y-%m-%d : %H")

match:
    $date_hour
outcome:
    $count = count_distinct(principal.ip)
order:
    $date_hour asc

dashboardQueries.name: dd3b00d9-993e-4a30-a6e2-32d1667142f4
dashboardQueries.query:
metadata.vendor_name="Corelight"
metadata.product_event_type = "conn"
about.resource.attribute.labels["capture_source"] = "vpcflow"
network.ip_protocol != "ICMP" OR (network.ip_protocol = "ICMP" AND re.regex(principal.ip, `.*:.*`))
((principal.location.name!="" OR principal.resource.product_object_id!="" OR principal.resource.name!="" OR principal.resource.attribute.labels.key = "org_id" OR
 principal.resource.attribute.labels.key = "sg_id" OR principal.resource.attribute.labels.key ="subnet_id" OR principal.resource.attribute.labels.key = "vpc_id" OR
 principal.resource.attribute.labels.key = "profile") OR
 (target.location.name!="" OR target.resource.product_object_id!="" OR target.resource.name!="" OR target.resource.attribute.labels.key = "org_id" OR
 target.resource.attribute.labels.key = "sg_id" OR target.resource.attribute.labels.key ="subnet_id" OR target.resource.attribute.labels.key = "vpc_id" OR
 target.resource.attribute.labels.key = "profile"))

match:
    principal.location.name, target.location.name
outcome:
    $total_bytes_sent = math.round(sum(cast.as_float(principal.labels["orig_ip_bytes"])/1073741824), 2)
    $count = count(network.session_id)
order:
    $total_bytes_sent desc
limit:
    20

dashboardQueries.name: 67588ccf-cc2e-4cce-b713-2fcd3e3d1bfb
dashboardQueries.query:

dashboardQueries.name: 2955bfa6-5912-41c8-b242-59af87d33941
dashboardQueries.query:
metadata.vendor_name="Corelight"
metadata.product_event_type = "conn"
about.resource.attribute.labels["capture_source"] = "vpcflow"
network.ip_protocol != "ICMP" OR (network.ip_protocol = "ICMP" AND re.regex(principal.ip, `.*:.*`))
additional.fields["direction"] != ""
$transport_port = strings.concat(if(network.ip_protocol = "EIGRP", "EIGRP", if(network.ip_protocol = "ESP", "ESP", if(network.ip_protocol = "ETHERIP", "ETHERIP",
            if(network.ip_protocol = "GRE", "GRE", if(network.ip_protocol = "ICMP" AND re.regex(principal.ip, `.*:.*`), "ICMP6", if(network.ip_protocol = "ICMP", "ICMP",
            if(network.ip_protocol = "IGMP", "IGMP", if(network.ip_protocol = "IP6IN4", "IP6IN4", if(network.ip_protocol = "PIM", "PIM", if(network.ip_protocol = "SCTP", "SCTP",
            if(network.ip_protocol = "TCP", "TCP", if(network.ip_protocol = "UDP", "UDP", if(network.ip_protocol = "VRRP", "VRRP", "UNKNOWN_IP_PROTOCOL"
            ))))))))))))), "/", cast.as_string(target.port))

match:
    principal.ip, target.ip, $transport_port

outcome:
    $first_alert_time = timestamp.get_timestamp(min(metadata.event_timestamp.seconds), "%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")
    $last_alert_time = timestamp.get_timestamp(max(metadata.event_timestamp.seconds), "%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")
    $total_duration = sum(network.session_duration.seconds)
    $total_bytes_sent = math.round(sum(cast.as_float(principal.labels["orig_ip_bytes"]))/1073741824, 2)
    $total_bytes_recv = math.round(sum(cast.as_float(target.labels["resp_ip_bytes"]))/1073741824, 2)
    $total_connections = count(network.session_id)
    $direction = array_distinct(additional.fields["direction"])
    $vpc_id = array(about.resource.product_object_id)

order:
    $total_connections desc

match:
    $transport_port
outcome:
    $count = count(network.session_id)
order:
    $count desc
limit:
    10
